text: 1. Hello, it is eggnog latte season! 2. This vertical pumpkin roll cake is incredible. 3. Anyone else ridiculously excited to take a cart and walk through target this week to look at the christmas things?! 4. I am living for all of the Wicked collabs that are coming out. There are so many! We can’t even wait to see the movie. 5. What’s something popular that you just don’t get?! The comment section is GOLD. 6. Along with the book tree I shared last week… I also want to try and cover my book shelves in christmas lights. I am an elf this year. 7. My 2024 gift guides are live with more coming this week! I love writing about what I love. 8. TV things!! The Martha doc. OMG. Everything I want and more. 9. Food and cooking superstitions. How fun.
html:
1. Hello, it is eggnog latte season!

2. This vertical pumpkin roll cake is incredible.

3. Anyone else ridiculously excited to take a cart and walk through target this week to look at the christmas things?!

4. I am living for all of the Wicked collabs that are coming out. There are so many! We can’t even wait to see the movie.

5. What’s something popular that you just don’t get?! The comment section is GOLD.

6. Along with the book tree I shared last week… I also want to try and cover my book shelves in christmas lights. I am an elf this year.

7. My 2024 gift guides are live with more coming this week! I love writing about what I love.

8. TV things!! The Martha doc. OMG. Everything I want and more.

9. Food and cooking superstitions. How fun.
